description: This file is the entry point for a React web application. It imports necessary modules, including React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes and renders the root React component within the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering React elements into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React element tree into the DOM node.
